.SH NAME
iio_dma_buffer_set_bytes_per_datum \- DMA buffer set_bytes_per_datum callback
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "int" iio_dma_buffer_set_bytes_per_datum
.BI "(struct iio_buffer *buffer "  ","
.BI "size_t bpd "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "buffer" 12
Buffer to set the bytes-per-datum for
.IP "bpd" 12
The new bytes-per-datum value
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
Should be used as the set_bytes_per_datum callback for iio_buffer_access_ops
struct for DMA buffers.
